INSERT INTO `comment` VALUES (1,'linus/7side.jpg','This is a memorial to seven victims. ','2006-09-15 00:55:39'),(2,'linus/barbiedeathcamp1.jpg','This is the Barbie Death Camp and Wine Bistro - DAM','2006-09-15 01:03:29'),(3,'linus/albertsons.jpg','I loved this sign at Albersons. It really showed that Burning Man is big business to these people. DAM','2006-09-15 01:04:35'),(4,'linus/barbiedeathcamp.jpg','This is another Barbie Death Camp picture, this time from a different angle. DAM','2006-09-15 01:05:06'),(5,'linus/bells.jpg','These were bells that were ringing by themselves. Each had a little motor in it run by the solar cell on the top. DAM','2006-09-15 01:05:57'),(6,'linus/bicycle1.jpg','This picture is an attempt to illustrate a narrative I was writing. We shall see how that works out. DAM','2006-09-15 01:06:45'),(7,'linus/bicycle2.jpg','This is another attempt to illustrate my narrative. DAM','2006-09-15 01:07:06'),(8,'linus/burning bellies.jpg','This is Kat of Terra Nova who organized (and is dancing with) the Burning Bellies.  - DAM','2006-09-15 01:09:15'),(9,'linus/burning snake.jpg','This is the giant metal snake during the day. -DAM','2006-09-15 01:09:50'),(10,'linus/camp.jpg','This is Bruno that first morning. -DAM','2006-09-15 01:10:19'),(11,'linus/jaywithmask2.jpg','I love this picture of Jay because it\'s of a beautiful woman, scantily clad but wearing a dust mask and goggles. The essense of Burning Man! -DAM','2006-09-15 01:11:13'),(12,'linus/davelater2.jpg','I would say this is the \"AFTER\" picture of me at Burning Man.  -DAM','2006-09-15 01:11:40'),(13,'linus/daveearly.jpg','This is the \"BEFORE\" picture of me at Burning Man. If I wasn\'t wearing a sarong it would be a better contrast with the \"AFTER\" picture. \"If wearing a sarong, I don\'t want to be right!\"  -DAM','2006-09-15 01:12:51'),(14,'linus/catscradle.jpg','I kind of like this layout, with the Waffle between the hands but the cameras I brought were too junky to be worth the trouble.  -DAM','2006-09-15 01:13:43'),(15,'linus/cathedral.jpg','The Cathedral. -DAM','2006-09-15 01:14:01'),(16,'linus/campsetup.jpg','This is us in the early stages of camp set up.  -DAM','2006-09-15 01:14:24'),(17,'linus/playawear.jpg','This is another cool picture of a prety girl wearing a mask. This was taken about 15 minutes before the white out.  -DAM','2006-09-15 01:15:08'),(18,'linus/nakedmenparade.jpg','This was the naked guy parade.  -DAM','2006-09-15 01:15:35'),(19,'linus/twister.jpg','This was an attempt to capture a dust devil. Not too bad considering the equipment.  -DAM','2006-09-15 01:16:31'),(20,'linus/virginbell.jpg','This is the virgin bell at the greeter station at the front gate. I think this is Candice. -DAM','2006-09-15 01:17:11'),(21,'linus/waffle.jpg','This is the view from inside this weird structure on the playa. There was a frequency generator inside that made low frequence noises. I probably should have gone out and moved the bike but it was hard to get in and out...  -DAM','2006-09-15 01:18:24'),(22,'linus/playa.jpg','I was trying to capture an image of the playa to give people an idea of what it was like. It reminds me but it doesn\'t really do the playa justice. -DAM','2006-09-15 01:19:39'),(23,'linus/barbiedeathcamp1.jpg','This shows barbies being herded into an oven.','2006-10-20 23:52:21');
