ot. She didn\'t even know the question, much less the answer. And that witch did it on purpose; she knew that Gem didn\'t hear the question.\r\n\r\n\"Could you repeat the question.\" \r\n\r\n\"Could you pay attention in class, please, Gem? The question is what is the function of a ribosome?\" \r\n\r\nGem had no clue and, except for the embarrassment of getting called out in class, couldn\'t care less. She expected to live a long and happy life without out ever knowing what a ribosome is. Gem opened her mouth to say \"I don\'t know\" \r\nbut she was interupted.\r\n\r\n\"It provides energy for the cell.\"\r\n\r\n\"Alan, I didn\'t ask you. I asked Gem.\" \r\n\r\n\"I know but Gem doesn\'t know the answer and we\'re just getting to the interesting part of the cell.\"\r\n\r\nGem was thrilled! Alan stood up for her and even got in trouble for it. She liked him even more!\r\n\r\n\r\n','2009-09-30','2009-09-30 18:27:20'),(492,90,'DAM','<ol>\r\n<li> more on ian\'s volunteer job with the homeless\r\n<li> rewrite bully, see 1/19\r\n<li> more about Ian and Alana\'s relationship in \"Ian And Alana Continue to Work \"\r\n<li>  danel has another talk with ian and tell him to stop being so up tight; yes you see what they don\'t but you need to USE that to do your job\r\n\r\n<ol><li>x the place where I talk about Ian staying to do his masters, add in a discussion of ian\'s style -- it\'s too informal for his advisor\r\n</ol>\r\n<li> He becomes much less carping\r\n<li> he gets a job and holds it down; it pays well but he hates it; but it\'s OK\r\n<li> At the end of the book, he hs published and it\'s doing well\r\n<li> You have to get these kids married at some point.\r\n\r\n<li>x ian and alana have a conversation during the vacation \r\n<li>x Ian has to do his research during the vacation\r\n<li>x Ian goes back after and has a conversation with his advisor -- he quits\r\n\r\n<li> x a series of scenes at the recruiting firm; check out note @ 1/19\r\n<ol><li> x He interacts with his c