,0,'2007-09-09','2007-09-09','Done','','2009-05-15 18:54:53'),(49,10,1,'Add a general select routine','A routine that accepts the following\r\n$command - an sql command\r\n$field - an array of fields\r\n$connector - \"and\" or \"or\"\r\n$where - an array of where clauses\r\n$order - an array of fields to order it by\r\n$set - key value pairs where the keys are all columns and the values are values for those\r\n\r\nThe routine then constructs a command that\'s basically\r\n$command.\" \".$field[0].\",\".$field[1]... \"where \".$where[0].\" \".$connector.\" \".$where[1]... \" order by \".$order[0].\",\".$order[1]\r\nIf it\'s an update or insert then we use the $set stuff. \r\n\r\nBasically, you load up these arrays and then call the routine. This allows for conditional field lists, where, order, and set clauses in routines. For complicated php situations. \r\n',1,5,0,0,'2007-08-03','2007-08-03','Done','','2009-05-15 18:54:53'),(50,10,1,'add the ability to delete records','You can\'t delete records from this interface ',1,4,0,0,'2007-08-03','2007-08-03','Done','','2009-05-15 18:54:53'),(51,20,1,'add the ability to create and clear the table','and you can\'t create the table ',1,4,0,0,'2007-08-03','2007-08-03','Done','','2009-05-15 18:54:53'),(52,30,1,'Allow for differentiation among fields','For starters, field lengths. Field types, both in the database AND in the web interface. Data stamps (if I could get those to work at all). ',1,4,0,0,'2007-08-03','2007-08-03','Done','','2009-05-15 18:54:53'),(53,0,1,'Add a link to the edit screen to allow you to go back to the main list if you don\'t want to edit it','',1,6,0,0,'2007-08-03','2007-08-03','Done','','2009-05-15 18:54:53'),(54,2,1,'delete the line that says how many records were found','',1,6,0,0,'2007-08-03','2007-08-03','Done','','2009-05-15 18:54:53'),(55,3,1,'change add and edit so that they use a table','',1,6,0,0,'2007-08-03','2007-08-03','Done','','2009-05-15 18:54:53'),(56,1,1,'remove finished items from the l