 do it. Once that person is chosen, however, they have total control and should not be second guessed based on my comments (real or imagined) or my writings nor by any other communications beforehand. In The Moment.\r\n\r\nGuidelines\r\nAlthough the designated person has all the power, it\'s an aweful position to put someone in. ',1,9,0,0,'2007-08-03','2007-08-03','Done','','2009-05-15 18:54:53'),(226,5,1,'email about insurance','we want to change to kaiser; find out how to do that and send email',1,9,0,0,'2007-08-03','2007-08-03','Done','','2009-05-15 18:54:53'),(227,0,1,'get a car','find a car for keith',1,9,0,0,'2007-08-03','2007-08-03','Done','','2009-05-15 18:54:53'),(228,15,1,'find a painter','contact a painter and set up a meeting',1,9,0,0,'2007-08-03','2007-08-03','Done','','2009-05-15 18:54:53'),(229,15,1,'get car maintained','',1,9,0,0,'2007-08-03','2007-08-03','Done','','2009-05-15 18:54:53'),(230,1,1,'car wash','',1,9,0,0,'2007-08-03','2007-08-03','Done','','2009-05-15 18:54:53'),(231,8,1,'make the description column shorter on the notes','The right hand side of the page is squished a bit because the descriptions are too wide. Constrain the descriptions and it will look good again...',1,20,0,0,'2007-08-03','2007-08-03','Done','','2009-05-15 18:54:53'),(441,20,1,'Fix design app so we have a notes link on the left','',1,9,0,0,'2007-09-09','2007-09-09','Done','','2009-05-15 18:54:53'),(439,20,1,'Fix mediation list','I want 5 separate lists instead of 8 columns',1,9,0,0,'2007-09-09','2007-09-09','Done','','2009-05-15 18:54:53'),(440,4,1,'Turnstyle: Add the numbers game pages','The numbers game gets it\'s own page with links to instance pages. \r\n\r\nThe important issue here is where we draw the line between public views and players. In the case of the numbers game the only thing that\'s really private is the users guess and that the user\'s personal history. If we made those two sections conditional we could show the same page for public and private -- but 